{"tid":2249510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧地利外長 比利時副首相中招","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:58:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"959b8ecfe12efe5bbfbc272fe8a20487e6a3dfc9","tid":2249510,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/OTMLP6CC6BCXRGOR4ASQ2IYS3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2FOTMLP6CC6BCXRGOR4ASQ2IYS3U%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=757312f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2FOTMLP6CC6BCXRGOR4ASQ2IYS3U%2F&h=2c005535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/OTMLP6CC6BCXRGOR4ASQ2IYS3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n奧地利外長 比利時副首相中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DgU8lsEkz68APncapunYzKw6rCc=/1332x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6D7XXCQQ5ZHKBE6V3XQ2WMDREM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDgU8lsEkz68APncapunYzKw6rCc%3D%2F1332x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6D7XXCQQ5ZHKBE6V3XQ2WMDREM.jpg&h=02af6962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■比利時外長維爾姆斯確診武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n比利時副首相兼外相維爾姆斯（Sophie Wilmes）前日表示確診患上武漢肺炎，是繼奧地利外長沙倫貝格（Alexander Schallenberg）後，第二位歐洲外長染疫，兩人上周一均在盧森堡出席歐盟外交事務委員會會議。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疫潮催生失落一代  英12萬輟學少年恐淪毒販<br />\n<br />\n在維爾姆斯宣佈檢測結果前，。。。。。。。。。，認為可能是在家庭圈子受感染。<br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯、法國外長勒德里昂、西班牙外相岡薩雷斯的檢測結果都是陰性反應，瑞典外相林德則會在有檢測報告前在家工作。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：貝理雅隔離未滿上餐廳 涉違防疫令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭破功 港口工確診<br />\n<br />\n至於兩周前宣佈再度擊敗病毒的新西蘭再次破功，新增一宗本地確診，患者是一名往返塔拉納基及奧克蘭的港口工人，他上周五出現病徵後檢測證實確診，當局已將患者的密切接觸者隔離。總理阿德恩指，當地毋須重新上調防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"4c847f2146ee0d91abf50711d2195675c79a5fa2","tid":2249510,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16caacbfb712b0f193ca0e6be201eff75363a1dc","tid":2249510,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎又記一功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次都咁精準跳上重要官員身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}